text: first solo budget session hit me hard – realizing you've got a handle on your own expenses outta nowhere...yeah that was my welcome-to-adulthood wake up call 😂
crashed servers at work - woke up fast!
biggest misconception? that we’re all earning crazy money straight outta college haha... trust me – still waiting for that 'coding millionaire' status 😂 patience is key!
techie = coffee addict stereotype rings pretty true here lol
debugging habits die hard - catch myself proofreading restaurant menus like it's code needing fixes 🤓 gotta laugh when waiters see me mumbling regex under my breath!
def agree that hitting milestones doesn’t mean ticking off society’s todos - just more time playing your own game 🎮🚀
